              <div class="font-display font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] text-sm">Sasha</div>
              <div class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-xs">Treacle, Basset Hound</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm leading-relaxed">"I would recommend Art all day long. From the moment he did our house visit and behaviour assessment he has been reliable, responsible and I have no hesitation in him taking my dog. Treacle loves him!"</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-brand-bg)] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
              <img src="/P3473/images/bolt.jpeg" alt="Bolt the dog" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-display font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] text-sm">Hannah</div>
              <div class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-xs">Bolt &amp; Max, 2020</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm leading-relaxed">"Honest, trustworthy, friendly and reliable and most importantly the dogs love him. Wonderful service that is also flexible to fit in with circumstance changes."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-brand-bg)] rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[var(--color-border)]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
              <img src="/P3473/images/mika.jpeg" alt="Mika the dog" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-display font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] text-sm">Jess</div>
              <div class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-xs">Mika, Cross, 2016</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-ink-soft)] text-sm leading-relaxed">"Art is professional and it is clear how much he loves spending time with and walking all of the dogs. Trustworthy and reliable caring for furry friends and when house sitting."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/P3473/testimonials" class="inline-block border-2 border-[var(--color-brand-accent)] text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-[var(--color-brand-accent)] hover:text-white transition-colors">Read All Reviews</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[var(--color-brand-accent)]">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🌙</div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl text-white mb-4">Ready to book a walk?</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200 mb-8 leading-relaxed">Get in touch with Art today to discuss your dog's needs. Serving Cranleigh, Ewhurst and Bramley.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center">
        <a href="/P3473/contact" class="bg-white text-[var(--color-brand-accent)] px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors">Book Now</a>
        <a href="tel:07792663847" class="bg-white/15 text-white border border-white/30 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-white/25 transition-colors">07792 663847</a>
      </div>
