          </div>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">Family-run dog walking in Cranleigh, Ewhurst and Bramley, Surrey. Art and Mandy.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-white text-sm mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Pages</div>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm">
